{"tid":578926,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《詩經》：〈王風．中谷有蓷〉，討論嘅字正字地位","createTime":"2018-03-03T06:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T17:45:08.000Z","uid":53209,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fc2d57f0a85ddb8459ebe1668858ddf212a5560d","tid":578926,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T06:13:33.000Z","msg":"中谷有蓷，暵其乾矣。 <br />\n有女仳離，<span style=\"color: red;\">嘅</span>其嘆矣。 <br />\n嘅其嘆矣，遇人之艱難矣！<br />\n<br />\n中谷有蓷，暵其脩矣。 <br />\n有女仳離，條其歗矣。 <br />\n條其歗矣，遇人之不淑矣！<br />\n<br />\n中谷有蓷，暵其濕矣。 <br />\n有女仳離，啜其泣矣。 <br />\n啜其泣矣，何嗟及矣！<br />\n-------<br />\npoint1,嘅自古已有，解慨，嘆息。<br />\n我地點解要用一個自古已有，而且唔同解釋既字作為 <br />\n<br />\n &lsquo;&rsquo;既&lsquo;&rsquo; 的正字呢?(我既，你既 入面既的意思，解作的)<br />\n-----<br />\npoint2<br />\n我既你既  只係粵語口語，實際上根本無正字存在，屬有音無字。<br />\n<br />\n----<br />\npoint3<br />\n粵語審音配詞字庫，漢語多功能字典 查無此字<br />\n<br />\n----<br />\npoint4<br />\n說文解字:嘅：嘆也。从口旣聲"},{"pid":"d6aa4971b0cb107d6fdc7dc35be1b6fb82b4774d","tid":578926,"uid":53209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T06:18:02.000Z","msg":"要求肥絲現身說法"},{"pid":"683a5480c94b94f2dd7e30cd25d203364a42081b","tid":578926,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T06:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537ddbfd3a2bc3d08dec2e54f04fcf4bb83ac57d","tid":578926,"uid":71237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T06:31:19.000Z","msg":"咁你可唔可以justify點解要打&quot;左&quot;字先?"},{"pid":"399013b351798f77fa47e91970a7733016e9a625","tid":578926,"uid":112198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T06:34:21.000Z","msg":"高質post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5656d714500509cc1a114058e9337421e1143e1e","tid":578926,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T06:36:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你可唔可以justify點解要打&quot;左&quot;字先?</blockquote><br />\n返上一個pos